Class IString

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.IDataValue

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEntity, IEntity, IValue

    public class IString
extends IDataValue
    Represents a string-value, with the actual value being represented by a primitive Java String value.
